title: Juwan Howard Joins the Show!
description:
Jalen & Jacoby talk to Michigan Coach and Fab Five teammate Juwan Howard before his upcoming Sweet 16 matchup with Villanova. Coach Howard breaks down player matchups as he goes head to head with the Wildcats. And he relives his favorite Fab Five moments with Jalen and how their confidence was equal to their skill level. Plus, what’s going on with the Warriors? Are they “playing stupid” like Draymond Green said or just missing Steph? All that and much more.
